Reasoning: The paper discusses the shallow and fragile knowledge on the Web and how it leads to forgetfulness of knowledge. This suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The mention of ontology matching suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL) as well.
